title: SR in 60: President Obama is calling today's Supreme Court decision in favor of his health care law a victory for hardworking Americans
text:
powered by Live SR in 60: President Obama is calling today's Supreme Court decision in favor of his health care law a victory for hardworking Americans 
Jun. 25, 2015 - 1:11 - President Obama is calling today's Supreme Court decision in favor of his health care law a victory for hardworking Americans. Justices upheld federal subsidies for 6.5 million subscribers. It is the second time the high court has made a major ruling validating Obamacare.
